name: Sausage & Peppers
description:
You might not associate Italian-American comfort food with “low carb,” but this dish is about to change that. Our paleo version of the Italian street-fair favorite sticks closely to the original, featuring seared sausage with roasted red and green peppers and onions topped with our delightfully simple marinara. On the side, we switch things up with a cauliflower rice that’s mixed with Italian mainstays tomato, garlic, and basil. 

All of the sausage in our meals is provided by Polidori, a 4th-generation, family-owned producer. Polidori uses only the finest cuts of pork with all-natural spices—no MSG or preservatives.
ingredients: Italian Sausage (Pork, Water, Salt, Spices, Paprika, Natural Flavoring), Cauliflower, Marinara Sauce (Diced Tomatoes (Tomatoes, Tomato Juice, Citric Acid, Calcium Chloride), Tomato Puree (Water, Tomato Paste), Olive Oil, Onions, Tapioca Starch, Spices, Garlic, Honey, Sea Salt, Salt, Citric Acid), Bell Peppers, White Onion, Tomatoes, Expeller Pressed Canola Oil, White Balsamic Vinegar (Wine Vinegar, Concentrated Grape Must), Garlic, Sea Salt, Honey, Dehydrated Garlic, Spices.

fa.description:
شما ممکن است فکر کنید غذای ایتالیایی-آمریکایی با کربوهیدرات کم یک شوخی بیش نیست، اما این غذا فکر شما را عوض خواهد کرد. مدل رژیمی ما از این غذای ایتالیایی بسیار شبیه به همان چیزیست که در خیابان‌های رم توسط دکه‌ها درست میشود. این غذا مخلوط شگفت انگیزی از سوسیس کباب‌شده، فلفل دلمه‌ای کباب‌شده سبز، نارنجی، زرد و قرمز، پیاز قرمز والبته سس مارینارا دست‌ساز ماست. در کنار این مخلوط، ما اوضاع را کمی عوض کرده و برنج گل‌کلم دار که با گوجه‌فرنگی ایتالیایی و سیر و ریحان طعم‌دار شده‌است را قرار داده‌ایم.

همه سوسیس‌های ما محصول آندره است که یکی از قدیمی‌ترین و معتمد‌ترین برندها در تولید سوسیس است. آندره تنها از بهترین تکه‌های گوشت گوسفند و مرغ استفاده می‌کند همراه با چاشنی‌های طبیعی و بدون هرگونه مواد نگه‌دارنده.
fa.displayName: سوسیس و فلفل دلمه‌ای همراه با برنج گل‌کلم - ‌گوجه‌فرنگی

name: Grilled Chicken Risotto
description: Based on an Italian classic, we created this meal to feature one of our favorite comforting fall flavors. Our chefs fold butternut squash purée and buttery Parmesan cheese into a creamy risotto made with oyster mushrooms and sautéed onions, creating a sweet-and-savory base for juicy grilled chicken and roasted butternut squash (yes, this dish has a double hit of butternut flavor). For a little extra freshness, try topping your dish with fragrant chopped parsley, a sprinkle of nutty grated Parmesan, and fresh cracked pepper.

name: Cod Cakes
description: Our chefs created this playful dish for fish lovers and fish dabblers alike. We balance cod’s delicate flavor with a vibrant mix of roasted veggies, Parmesan cheese, and fragrant herbs and spices, and top the fish cakes with a tangy chipotle vinaigrette. We cooked up two complementary sides to round out this high-fiber dish: roasted herb potatoes made with nutrient-filled, skin-on red potatoes and a colorful Southern succotash of lima beans, corn, and bell peppers. Bring out the bright flavors with a squeeze of fresh lemon or a sprinkling of red pepper flakes.

name: Carved Turkey
description:
For this festive turkey dish, we wanted to capture all the comforts of a home-cooked holiday feast. Our all-natural turkey is slow roasted until super tender, and topped with a thick diced-apple compote for a bit of sweet contrast. Speaking of sweet—we prepare our mashed sweet potatoes with a touch of honey, making them a perfect partner for the super-savory Brussels sprouts mixed with all-natural, uncured bacon and roasted mushrooms.

To further enhance the play on sweet and savory, try sprinkling a little cinnamon on your sweet potatoes and adding shredded Parmesan to the Brussels sprouts.
ingredients: Turkey (Turkey Breast, Water, Canola Oil, Salt, Black Pepper), Sweet Potatoes, Brussels Sprouts, Mushrooms, Apples, Onion, Honey, Bacon (Pork, Water, Less than 2% Salt, Vinegar, Celery Powder), Maple Syrup, Apple Juice (Water, Apple Juice Concentrate, Ascorbic Acid), Expeller Pressed Canola Oil, Water, Chicken Stock (Chicken Broth, Natural Flavors, Mirepoix Stock (Carrot, Onion and Celery Juices), Gelatin, White Wine), Cassava Flour, Sea Salt, Xanthan Gum, Dehydrated Garlic, Spices.
